      "creation_date" : 1683054550,
      "post_id" : 46025437,
      "comment_id" : 134306993,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Once the expression becomes even slightly more complex though, yes I would probably switch to a Lambda for readability. E.g., <code>.map(MyType::getProp).filter(Objects.isNull)</code> feels kinda awkward compared to just <code>.filter(x -&gt; x.getProp() == nulll)</code>. Plus, I think the chained <code>map</code>/<code>filter</code> calls might actually be slower than the single <code>filter</code>. But again, we&#39;re talking about a super micro difference, and I&#39;ve never actually benchmarked it."
