      "comment_id" : 135525825,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "One of the tenants of streams usage I follow is to keep the individual operations within the stream and distinct.   There may be a small time difference between the mapping and the filter however in the 80% (percentages may vary) of cases I&#39;d argue for the added clarity."
