      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "From <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/Objects.html#isNull-java.lang.Object-\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">the docs</a>: This method exists to be used as a Predicate, filter(Objects::isNull)"
